title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Running Back
content: Running Back returns to the Featured Series, turning local roads into a makeshift gridiron where Attackers and Defenders attempt to reach the opposition’s end zone at risk of life and limb. Whichever side you’re on, you’ll roll away with 2X GTA$ and RP after the final whistle.
